query:
UPDATE completed_job
            SET 
                raw_code = d.raw_code,
                raw_lock = d.raw_lock,
                raw_flow = d.raw_flow
            FROM job_definition d
            WHERE completed_job.id = d.id
                AND completed_job.workspace_id = d.workspace_id
                AND completed_job.id = ANY($1)
                AND completed_job.workspace_id = $2
